SUMMARY:Interchange Message: WEMBLEY PARK STATION: Friday 15 August\, 
 between 2230 and 2340\, and Saturday 16 August\, between 2230 and 2325\, 
 the station will be busy due to concerts at Wembley Stadium. The Bridge 
 Road entrance will be exit only until the queue to enter the station 
 clears. Entry to the station\, including step-free access via lift\, will 
 be via Olympic Way. Please allow extra time for your journey
